---
title: One-Pot Cowboy Turkey & Bean Chili with Jalapeño & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: A good chili has well-seasoned meat, creamy beans (if you're not from Texas, that is), and tender veggies. A great chili, however, has all that and comes together in one pot in under an hour—and this chili is one of the greats. Top-notch turkey-fied bowls are adorned with some delicious fixings: smoky red pepper crema and sliced jalapeño. If you’ve got some on hand, why not sprinkle some crumbled tortilla chips on top for crunch?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-cowboy-turkey-bean-chili-3969966b.jpg
